  "text": "The function g guarantees the convergence of the vector sequence generated by the algorithm (see Section 3.6). It also reduces the difference between good and very good values providing a smoothing of the scores. This function has a similar role as the sigmoid in backpropagation neural networks [CITATION_1] .",
